Lab 2 â€“ Simple UNIX Shell

Files:
- myshell.c   : main shell loop, parsing, execution
- utility.c  : internal commands and helpers
- myshell.h  : shared definitions
- makefile   : builds shell with `make`
- readme     : documentation

Features:
- Internal commands: cd, clr, dir, environ, echo, help, pause, quit
- External command execution via fork/exec
- I/O redirection: <, >, >>
- Background execution with &
- Batch mode: ./myshell batchfile
- Environment variables: shell, parent
